erest for Sponsored Projects    Prohibition of Sexual Assault and Retaliation   Cash Handling Controls   Use of Alcoholic Beverages    Hazing    CARE Assessment Team and Involuntary Student Medical Withdrawal   Student Complaint   Pages1 2 next \u203a last »  Last updated:   Date: 2013-10-07Action: RevisionComments: Revised to comply with changes in the federal law.  Policy effective 10/7/2013.     Date: 2012-09-26Action: Format Only     Date: 2012-01-31Action: RevisionComments: Revised to comply with recent changes to Title IX.  Effective 1/31/2012.     Date: 2009-08-01Action: RevisionComments: Revised to remove academic integrity issues from the Code, include the option for students to utilize Peer Advocates in the judicial process, and clarify group conduct vs. student/individual conduct. Effective 08/01/2009.     Date: 2003-10-01Action: Revision     Date: 2001-08-01Action: Revision     Date: 2000-07-01Action: Revision     Date: 1999-08-01Action: Revision     Date: 1998-08-01     Date: 1996-08-01Action: Revision     Date: 1991-05-01Action: New Policy    Top                          Main Menu Home FAQ Policy manual Resources Policy updates About the Policy Office  University Links  MyUNT Blackboard EagleConnect UNT Directory UNT Map UNT Calendar Jobs at UNT Give to UNT  Email & Phone   policy@unt.edu  940-565-4535    University Policy Office    Find UNT on Google Maps   1155 Union Circle #311277           Denton, Texas 76203-5017   Visitor Information  Call us Email Us UNT Map               Apply now Schedule a tour Get more info   Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Electronic Accessibility | Required Links | UNT Home ©2017 University of North Texas Required Links         
